{"tid":2449038,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中方稱應以科學和建設性態度看待沙塵天氣並避免炒作","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T11:09:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3286ead9e6f60e43b3536fa96fd906cbebb422e5","tid":2449038,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"中方稱應以科學和建設性態度看待沙塵天氣並避免炒作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580883-20210316.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580883-20210316.htm&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQ2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=8101c898\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580883-20210316.htm&h=d5d3ad62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580883-20210316.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓傳媒日前指出，南韓空氣污染惡化，源於中國的沙塵暴。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人趙立堅指，根據中國監測機構分析，今次沙塵天氣源自中國境外，中國只是途經站，中國輿論亦沒有因為蒙古可能是上一站而加以指責。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅認為應以科學和建設性態度，看待相關問題，正面引導輿論，避免不必要炒作和輕易扣帽子，中方願與國際社會攜手推進全球環境治理保護。"},{"pid":"a82525a64288c2faf9897cab6926982550b9a1cc","tid":2449038,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"草木皆兵"}]}